          "Refuse entirely — investigations can never be expanded once started",
          "Decline to action outside the existing ToR. Explain that a formal ToR amendment with documented lawful basis is required. Researching the spouse without basis violates GDPR Article 6; offshore account searches require specific legal authority.",
